    "body": "You want this, but also ability to do it with an offset. What if the offset is incompatible to the inferred_freq, raise?\n\n```\nIn [17]: pd.Period('1990q1')\nOut[17]: Period('1990Q1', 'Q-DEC')\n\nIn [18]: pd.Period('1990q1') + 2\nOut[18]: Period('1990Q3', 'Q-DEC')\n```\n"
